<%= @user.greeting %>

<% if @period.auto_open_time %>
Job choosing is coming up on <%= l(@period.auto_open_time, format: :short_date) %>!
<% else %>
Job choosing is coming up soon!
<% end %>

You have <%= @synopsis.user_regular_got %> pre-assigned hours and your quota is <%= @synopsis.user_adjusted_quota %>, so you need to pick <%= @synopsis.user_need %> regular hours.

<% if @synopsis.user_full_community_hours.any? %>
You are also expected to choose <%= @synopsis.user_full_community_hours.map { |job, hours| "#{hours} #{job.title} hours" }.join(", ") %>.
<% end %>

<% if @period.staggered? && @synopsis.user_need > 0 %>
Your round schedule is as follows:
<% @synopsis.rounds.each do |round| %>
* At <%= l(round[:starts_at], format: :regular_time).strip %> <%= round[:limit] ? "you can pick up to #{round[:limit]} hours" : "you can finish choosing" %>.
<% end %>
<% elsif @period.auto_open_time %>
Choosing begins at <%= l(@period.auto_open_time, format: :regular_time).strip %>.
<% end %>

Thanks for your participation!
